Module org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql
Package org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql.tools

Class GenericSemanticValidatorHelper

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql.tools.GenericSemanticValidatorHelper
All Implemented Interfaces:
SemanticValidatorHelper
public class GenericSemanticValidatorHelper extends Object implements SemanticValidatorHelper
An implementation of SemanticValidatorHelper that uses JPQLQueryContext to return the required information and Hermes SPI.

Provisional API: This interface is part of an interim API that is still under development and expected to change significantly before reaching stability. It is available at this early stage to solicit feedback from pioneering adopters on the understanding that any code that uses this API will almost certainly be broken (repeatedly) as the API evolves.

Since:
2.4
Version:
2.5
